Dialogs.Dialog: You know, I met someone I like.
Oh？ What？ Do you mean the musician？
I'm not sure if it's a character in a novel or a game.
I mean… it's not a quiz or anything.
（▲小早川＊▲… What's the meaning of what you were talking about earlier？）
You don't have any idea what I'm talking about？ Sigh… Rinko's worried about you.
What's that all about？ Yeah, I'm worried about this！
… I'm sorry. I can't believe I took that so seriously.
（▲小早川＊▲… I can't do anything because I'm too worried.）
First of all, calm down. Now, close your eyes.
You've got to be kidding me！ No way！ I am so sorry…
"I met someone I like." "Oh, come on, it's April Fool's Day！" I thought you'd…
… You think I must be really stupid at this point, don't you？
Quite a bit. But I don't mind that about you. I'm sorry. Please forgive me.
Oh！ It is Golden Week, isn't it？
Yeah. The three days from the 3rd to the 5th.
I heard if couples kissed every day during it, for a long time, their love would progress rapidly.
You know what I mean. Long-lasting kisses.
（So, the one that goes on forever？）
Don't be so ridiculous to take it so seriously.
（Then why did you tell me that？）
So, were you going for it？
The Golden Week kissing. Don't you remember？
I don't think this changes anything.
（I really feel like if we went through with it, I could have strengthed our bond, ▲小早川＊▲…）
I don't really care, so it's fine.
The Golden Week kiss. I'd forgotten after all.
I told you I don't care.
（Today is they're opening the pool. They're joining our grades in it, so I'll see ▲小早川＊▲…）
No, I think it's… okay, ▲小早川＊▲！
I don't know what you mean. Why don't you speak up？
Of everyone here, ▲小早川＊▲ is still the cutest girl.
I'm not exactly cool with being compared to others.
（I'm looking forward to more of this class！）
（Today is they're opening the pool. They're joining our grades in it, so I'll see ▲小早川＊▲…）
Don't stare at me like some pervert.
But, I wasn't… Um, maybe I didn't think I was staring.
If you get any closer, I'll kick you.
And if I catch you staring at the other girls, I'll get a teacher and say you're harassing them.
Would it be better to be kicked？
（I'm looking forward to more of this class！）
（Today is they're opening the pool. They're joining our grades in it, so I'll see ▲小早川＊▲…）
Hehe. It's refreshing to be in the school pool.
Don't stare so much. There are people around.
（I'm looking forward to more of this class！）
If you're not busy, come hang out with me.
It's just a pain out there. Let's read something. It'll be like being on library duty.
Because everyone is just playing in the pool, they won't care what we do.
How long can you stay underwater？
I don't know… maybe a minute？
Then, try to go for three minutes. If you can, I'll give you some potato chips I keep in the library.
Triple the time for a miniscule reward！？
No complaining！ Come on, come on.
Huh？ Why are you asking me that？
Because when everyone's wearing the same swimsuit… well I look… you know.
Really？ I wouldn't know, because I'm not really looking at anyone but ▲小早川＊▲.
Hehe. Don't try to be so cool about it.
I thought the pool would be a total pain, but it's pretty nice. It's like free time from class.
I've had enough rest. I think I'll go for a swim sometime.
I'm not doing that. Come on, let's go.
Sorr. I didn't know you'd be that surprised.
I thought I was going to stop breathing. I'm… I need CPR.
Idiot！ Of course not！ You big dummy！
（Pool class is a piece of cake…）
I was… I'll tickle you as payback！
Hey, hey！ Don't go saying stuff like that out loud！
I wonder if houses with small children decorate bamboo branches and make wishes.
Yes… well, there are a lot of places that do that, aren't there？
I see. You have a younger brother too, right？
Yeah. That's why I'm having trouble.
Hey, about Tanabata earlier. What were you concerned about？
Well… doesn't it look good for Rinko to make a wish on a strip of paper？
Is that so？ I wouldn't expect ▲小早川＊▲ to be into that.
There's a lot to consider, but there's a lot to Rinko.
Hmm. So you're wondering if you should go celebrate with him for your brother's sake？
Yes. It's a tug-of-war between affection and attitude.
I'm not sure I understand. What do you mean？
It's hard to explain the… obsession！
So, Tanabata. I've decided what I'm going to do.
Oh. Emotion won out, didn't it？
I see. I hope you have fun with it.
Yeah, I'm sure it'll be fine.
▲小早川＊▲. You're really mature when you're dealing with your brother, huh？
You're always like a normal adult, right？ So be like a true boyfriend about it.
Then it's also thanks to me.
I got carried away. But, yeah. I guess I will spend it with my brother. I appreciate it, so thanks.
（I'm done… It's such a hassle to come to school just for this, the first day of school…）
▲小早川＊▲. You can't just go out there like that. Even though we've just met.
Oh, man. My boyfriend is so lonely…
（I'm done… It's such a hassle to come to school just for this, the first day of school…）
I don't have anything in particular to do.
Then why not？ You can at least help me pass the time.
（I'm done… It's such a hassle to come to school just for this, the first day of school…）
Somehow, I came. It's nice once in a while, isn't it？
（Hmm. What a pain. The first of school.）
It's a bother, the first day of school.
… That's what I thought. Am I wrong？
Because I was thinking the same thing.
（Hmm. What a pain. The first of school.）
Don't look so gloomy. It makes me feel gloomy, too.
Oh, I'm sorry. But you don't want to come, do you？
Of course. You don't have to say it, so don't.
（Hmm. What a pain. The first of school.）
Hey, do you want to go to the arcade？
You've been practicing a lot, haven't you？
I'm sure it'sa lot of work, but since you're here, why don't you get some results？ I'll watch.
Well, I'm not really up for it, but I'm forced into a three-legged race.
Haha, I see. Well, just give it your best.
But I had to find a partner, too.
Oh, I see. Okay, well, let's get out of here together.
That's obvious. Well, let's get a little practice in.
Hmm, what？ Well, let's do this.
It's nothing！ … You've got a lot of energy, you know.
Oh, last place… Are you and Rinko compatible in this type of thing？
I think we can do well together. It's more a matter of physical strength.
It's Rinko's fault. You were trying so hard.
It's okay. It'll be a good memory for me.
Even though we came in last？
It's something I got to do with ▲小早川＊▲. So it's something I will cherish, regardless.
Just kidding. Thank you, though. It was nice of you to help me out…
Do you do anything for Halloween？
Oh, that's today. I don't have any plans or anything.
That's right. It's a pain to go through all the process to put on a fancy custume.
Maybe so, but it would be fun to be able to…
Why？ What do you have planned, ▲小早川＊▲？
I don't have any plans. But I wonder what I could do…
（There's nothing on TV. What should I do…？）
▲小早川＊▲？ What's going on？ You're here all of a sudden.
What？ I can't come visit you？
It's not like that. At any rate, go away.
So, what's going on？ What are you doing today？
Well. I'm gonna go get ready. Don't come in yet.
Well, what was it？ If it's not candy, I'm going to kick you！
I don't care if it's not candy…
That's… So, that's what I was pondering about Halloween.
Oh, well. Rinko had a lot of fun. Did you？
I was either embarrassed or nervous…
I barged in on you and sent you on your way. I'm sorry.
No, that's not necessary. I'll see you later.
（You did a great job on the committee, huh？ I hope it will be a success…）
（Let's take a look at ▲小早川＊▲'s class…）
Err… What's going on in in your class？
Exhibition of historical materials of Towano City.
Ugh, I'm not going to do it.
Why not？ It's easy. You're steering committee, right？ Are you busy？
I don't have that much work to do that day.
When I skipped all the preperatons, the teacher made me tout for the event. It's so boring…
（Poor girl… but she got what she deserved…）
（I'm glad the festival went off without a hitch. All that's left is the party.）
▲小早川＊▲. You changed your clothes, didn't you？
But the festival was a success, right？ It's all thanks to you guys.
I don't know if it's because of me or not, but I'm glad it was successful as well.
Hmm. You know what？ Let's hang out.
I'd like you to go somewhere with me.
There's no one here. The rooftop is a nice place, but isn't very popular.
Yeah. That's why I called you… here at that time, too.
It's a place I like, and no one will bother me, so I said I'd stick around… here.
I'm reminded of it every time I come here. I'm not comfortable here anymore, and it's not good for me.
I don't care about that. It's more about… how I'm remembering it again.
Can I do what I did back then？
Yeah. Summer school starts today. Haha…
Hey, I wonder how we can get rid of summer school. Maybe you break all the windows in he school now？
It's not just a summer course. It's the end of my student life.
Good morning. I hope your summer course will be over soon！
Yeah, I'm sick of summer school.
I mean, already？ It's like you didn't want to do it from the get-go.
I don't want to get into the details.
It's hot. Why bother with summer school when it's hot like this？
Good morning. I'm tired of summer school. Think we can skip it？
I know how you feel, but you've got to be patient.
Yeah. Did you know？ The winter semester starts today.
Eh？ Yeah. That's why you're here today, right？
Does it look like Rinko wants to take a winter course？
You should have done someting abot it before today. It's unreasonable…
Good morning. We're starting winter school today. Right or wrong？
You would think it feels right…
Hey, don't you think you did good enough to pass this course when you woke up freezing this morning？
Rinko might have caught a cold.
What？ Should you even be going today？
… Sorry, I lied. I wish my mom would have bought it, too.
I wish I could be saying good night right now.
（What do you want me to do？…）
Yeah. Spring semester starts today. I wonder how many times I'll doze off…
Alright, spring semester. I'll do my best from here on.
Good morning. Spring semester starts today. Dont you wish it would just fly right on by？
You're right. It's not that short.
That's right. I checked over and over again.
Alright. I'll try not to fall asleep today.
Oh？ Giving that a shot, huh？
That's what I thought last time, too.
Good morning. I guess the course is nearly over.
You think so…？ I'm not sure it's even close.
Oh, by the way, ▲小早川＊▲. Did you hear about the contest？
The swimsuit contest. They're going to do it.
Rinko's got nothing to do with it.
Surprisingly, it could be that ▲小早川＊▲ might be chosen to participate, you know？
I'm glad that to hear that…
I don't want to be a spectacle.
You don't like it, right？ Your girlfriend being in that type of thing.
It's complicated. But it… it's good. It gives more bragging rights about your girlfriend.
